docs {
  ## Get Sync Committee Messages

  Get sync committee messages known by the node but not necessarily incorporated into any block.

  ### Response (200)
  ```json
  {
    "data": [
      {
        "slot": "1",
        "beacon_block_root": "0xcf8e0d4e9587369b2301d0790347320302cc0943d5a1884560367e8208d920f2",
        "validator_index": "42",
        "signature": "0x8a2f4c6e8b0d1f3a5c7e9012b4d6f8a0c2e4168a0b2d4f6a8c0e2143658a7b9c0d2e4f6a8b0c2d4e6f8a0b2c4d6e8f0a2b4c6d8e0f2a4b6c8d0e2f4a6b8c0d2e4f6a8b0c2d4e6f8a0b2c4d6e8f0a2b4c6d8e0f2a4b6c8d0"
      }
    ]
  }
  ```
}
